## Project-A3 Explorer Module Architecture
**Status:** approved
**Tags:** stack:both

```mermaid
graph TB
    BE[GET /api/forge/project/tree] -->|TreeNode[]| TV[TreeView.vue]
    BE2[GET /api/forge/project/file] -->|bytes + MIME| PV[Preview Pane]
    TV -->|select| PV
    TV -->|filter| FT[Client-side filter]
    UC[useProject.ts] -->|projectName| NR[NavRail label]
```

- Tree API returns recursive `TreeNode` with `node_type: "file" | "folder"`
- File API validates path stays within project directory (blocks `..` and absolute paths)
- Preview pane uses `<pre>`, `<img>`, `<iframe>`, or download link based on MIME guess

